//“This drought is a terrible affair, your highness. When you decide it’s gone on long enough, you know our rates.”//
<div align="right">—[[Taelyn Lyrandar]], envoy of the Raincallers Guild</div>

Masters of [[weather magic|control weather]], this [[Lyrandar]] guild also includes un[[mark|dragonmark]]ed architects and engineers who construct canals, aqueducts, reservoirs, and [[storm spire]]s. Many of the members are constantly on the move, traveling from place to place according to climate and season. In addition, Raincallers often serve as traveling emissaries of House [[Lyrandar]], and are trained in the arts of diplomacy.
